Name: Metal Gear Solid V: The Phantom Pain

Achievements.Name: Beekeeper
Achievements.Description: Complete "WHERE DO THE BEES SLEEP?" mission.

Achievements.Name: Apprentice
Achievements.Description: Complete a mission using a Combat Unit staff member.

Achievements.Name: Elite
Achievements.Description: Complete all missions with an S rank.

Achievements.Name: Captured
Achievements.Description: Capture an outpost or guard post.

Achievements.Name: Platoon
Achievements.Description: Increase Mother Base staff to 50 or more personnel.

Achievements.Name: Battalion
Achievements.Description: Increase Mother Base staff to 250 or more personnel.

Achievements.Name: Architect
Achievements.Description: Construct all available platforms for Mother Base.

Achievements.Name: Prosperity
Achievements.Description: Earn a total of 10,000,000 GMP or more.

Achievements.Name: Truth
Achievements.Description: Complete "TRUTH: THE MAN WHO SOLD THE WORLD" mission.

Achievements.Name: Trusty Steed
Achievements.Description: Raise bond with D-Horse to the maximum.

Achievements.Name: Man's Best Friend
Achievements.Description: Raise bond with D-Dog to the maximum.

Achievements.Name: War Buddy
Achievements.Description: Raise bond with Quiet to the maximum.

Achievements.Name: Collector
Achievements.Description: Obtain all blueprints and key items.
